;; This example gives you a small number of
;; volume presets that can be toggled with
;; one hand (if you enable the option to use
;; right option as an extra fn key):

/*
$p::FnKeyCall("p", "VolumeSet", "0")
$[::FnKeyCall("[", "VolumeSet", "33")
